# AgentSpace — root env for the SECRET, server-side values (orchestrator + gateway).
# Copy to an untracked `.env` and fill in. NEVER commit real keys.
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# `.env` / `.env*.local` are gitignored. These are NOT EXPO_PUBLIC_ — they stay
# server-side (the mobile app never sees them). Mobile config lives in
# apps/mobile/.env.example.

# BYOK provider key for the Model Gateway smoke test (SETUP.md S-4 → VERIFICATION V-6),
# and for running the orchestrator against a real model (V-7/V-8). The smoke harness
# reads <PROVIDER>_API_KEY for the default model's provider (anthropic → ANTHROPIC_API_KEY).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Optional: key-encryption-key for the gateway's encrypted BYOK store (base64, 32 bytes).
# Only needed if you exercise the EncryptedKeyStore path (the envResolver path doesn't).
# Generate one with:  openssl rand -base64 32
# AGENTSPACE_GATEWAY_KEK=

# Optional: point the orchestrator at a specific server/db (defaults are local).
# AGENTSPACE_STDB_HOST=wss://maincloud.spacetimedb.com
# AGENTSPACE_STDB_DB=agentspace-hpm58
